# FortiGate Device Configuration
# Format: IP_ADDRESS, API_TOKEN, NAME (optional)
#
# API Token Setup:
#   1. Log into FortiGate GUI
#   2. System > Administrators > Create New > REST API Admin
#   3. Set admin profile with sysgrp read-write permissions
#   4. Restrict trusted hosts to your management subnet
#   5. Copy the generated API token
#
# 192.168.1.1, fmtXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX, HQ-FortiGate
# 192.168.2.1, fmtYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYY, Branch-1
# 10.0.0.1, fmtZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZ, DC-Primary
